    ElasticSearchController

    public static class ElasticSearchController.GetParticipantByUsernameTask
extends android.os.AsyncTask<java.lang.String,java.lang.Void,Participant>
    AsyncTask that gets participants from ElasticSearch. Taken from CMPUT301 ElasticSearch LonelyTwitter Jest Lab.

    Works only for grabbing one participant at a time.

    Calling execute(String username) on an instance of GetParticipantByUsernameTask will search for documents under the username argument.
